485/The-critical-study-of-biblical-literature-exegesis-and-hermeneutics">The critical study of biblical literature: exegesis and hermeneutics</a><ul><li class="lv2" data-section="73485" data-toc="73486"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73485/The-critical-study-of-biblical-literature-exegesis-and-hermeneutics#toc73486">Nature and significance</a></li><li class="lv2" data-section="73485" data-toc="73487"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73485/The-critical-study-of-biblical-literature-exegesis-and-hermeneutics#toc73487">Critical methods</a><ul><li class="lv3" data-section="73488" data-toc="73488"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73488/Textual-criticism">Textual criticism</a></li><li class="lv3" data-section="73488" data-toc="73489"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73488/Textual-criticism#toc73489">Philological criticism</a></li><li class="lv3" data-section="73490" data-toc="73490"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73490/Literary-criticism">Literary criticism</a></li><li class="lv3" data-section="73491" data-toc="73491"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73491/Tradition-criticism">Tradition criticism</a></li><li class="lv3" data-section="73491" data-toc="73492"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73491/Tradition-criticism#toc73492">Form criticism</a></li><li class="lv3" data-section="73491" data-toc="73493"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73491/Tradition-criticism#toc73493">Other types of exegetical critical techniques</a><ul><li class="lv4" data-section="73491" data-toc="73494"><a href="http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/64496/biblical-literature/73491/Tradition-criticism#toc73494">Redaction criticism</a></li><li class="l